## Description {#details}

The return value from 128-bit hashes.

Stored in little endian order, although the fields themselves are in native endianness.

Definition at line 64 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/support/xxhash-h">xxhash.h</a>.
